Every law is set by a sovereign person or a sovereign body of persons to a member or members of the independent politica] society wherein that person or body is sovereign or supreme: it is set by a monarch or sovereign number to a person or persons in a state of subjection to its author. A Sovereign is a determinate human superior, who receives habitual obedience or submission from the bulk of a given society, and is not in the habit of yielding obedience to a like superior.
